                <p>I thank all reviewers for their detailed reading od my paper, their encouraging words, and their very useful criticism that was critical to improving the argument!</p>
                <p> </p>
                <p> I have addressed all concerns, which means, in detail: The most important point of criticism shared by all reviewers was a certain gap between the lead hypothesis on convergences between complicities in totalitarianism and involvement in neoliberalism on the one hand, and the focus on distancing on the other hand. I have addressed this absolutely right observation by: 
                    <list list-type="order">
                        <list-item>
                            <p>Improving the framing so as to differentiate the comprehensive background of my reading from the element of that background that can actually be addressed in a paper (see Introduction).</p>
                        </list-item>
