                            <p>Added a substantial segment to the part &#x201c;Complicity in and beyond the Law&#x201d; explaining how the broader frame and the question of distance correlate, and I come back to it in paragraphs added to the readings of Fritsch and Jelinek.</p>
                        </list-item>
                    </list> 
            </p>
                <p> Further, smaller points have been addressed as follows: 
                    <list list-type="bullet">
